				<h2>Extract Zips</h2>
				<p>You should now have two zip files:
				<ol><li>Your site backup</li>
				<li>The add-on download</li>
				</ol>
				</p>
				<p>Extract both to a convenient location. (After this step, you should see both the zip file and the extracted folders in your directory.)</p>
			
				   <div class="tree clt">
<ul>
  <li>backup.zip</li>
  <li>extracted backup folder</li>
  <li>add-on.zip</li>
